comment: Hill (IND) dislodges Love (CLE) and prevents him from securing the rebound.
Love (CLE) contests the putback by Hill (IND) and the contact does not affect his play at the basket.
Scola (IND) clamps Love's (CLE) arm and prevents him from securing the rebound.
Irving (CLE) sets the screen on Hill (IND) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Thompson (CLE) bumps Hibbert (IND) and the contact affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Love (CLE) does not prevent Hibbert (IND) from attempting to retrieve the rebound with the contact.
Miles (IND) commits a take foul on Smith (CLE).
